N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 ยง 256.3 - Fences and enclosures

State Regulations

Holders shall be protected by suitable fencing or other
adequate means shall be provided for preventing access to holder structures by
unauthorized persons. Notes
